      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORNHILL BOOMER (1) filled a minor placing last start at Geelong behind Azzurro Wren (26.38) in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Has the pace to be prominent. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Good form should continue. FIVE JACKS (4) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (35.28) in a Restricted WIN at Sandown. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. BAKALI SURPRISE (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 6th and beaten 5 lengths at Shepparton (26.01). Form here at this distance is strong including zero wins. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. DEVON RUSLIE (2) should be thereabouts.",
